snippet.textDisplay:
What a beautiful song!
I think a prayer is beautiful no matter which religion/language/country it is being prayed in. "Ho teri nazren karam to yeh mushkil bhi tal jayegi"- No one on this planet has to be of a certain religion/country to understand this.
Shafqat Amanat Ali saab just puts out his heart when he sings. AJ's "Khaki Banda" was a hit from last season and he's got another hit this season (I know, I am calling this a hit just 40 minutes after it coming live).
Thanks Strings for season 10.

I am going back to playing this song in loop until the next one comes out :)
